WEBVTT

00:00:17.600 --> 00:00:18.640
When I was a kid

00:00:19.010 --> 00:00:22.650
The disaster we worried about most was a nuclear war

00:00:23.810 --> 00:00:29.410
That's why we had a barrel like this down in our basement
filled with cans of food and water

00:00:30.700 --> 00:00:33.5008
Nuclear attack came
We were supposed to go downstairs

00:00:33.700 --> 100:00:36.020
Hunker down and eat out of that barrel
